name: Intersection of Main St and Eisenhower Dr
description: The intersection of Main Street and Eisenhower Drive, a hub of bustling activity. You are at the intersection of Main St and Eisenhower Dr. Main St continues its journey to the east and west, a ribbon of charming commerce. Eisenhower Dr stretches to the south, disappearing into a neighborhood of brand new homes. The air is filled with the sound of happy chatter and the occasional honk of a brand new Studebaker.
